---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Asteris Pro Patterns. 73 premium block patterns for the Asteris theme."
  description="73 net-new block patterns the free Asteris theme doesn't ship. 8 niche page templates, 9 multimedia templates, 16 audio/video sections, 11 premium e-commerce patterns, 8 heroes, 7 composites. Founder pricing locked for life."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">★ Asteris Pro Patterns</span>
      <h1>Premium patterns for the<br>Asteris theme.</h1>
      <p class="lead">73 net-new block patterns the free theme doesn't ship. Drop them onto any page, replace the placeholder content, ship. No code, no design system to learn.</p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a href="#pricing" class="btn-primary">See pricing →</a>
        <a href="#whats-inside" class="btn-secondary">What's inside</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="whats-inside" class="categories">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">What's in the box</h2>
      <div class="cat-grid">
        <div class="cat-card">
          <div class="cat-num">19</div>
          <h3>Niche page templates</h3>
          <p>Photographer. Music artist. Conference. Author. Salon. Fitness studio. Tutorial library. Resume. Documentation. Sales page. Webinar. Lead magnet. Job posting. Case study. Thank you. Maintenance. vs Competitor. Restaurant menu. Coach.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cat-card">
          <div class="cat-num">9</div>
          <h3>Multimedia page templates</h3>
          <p>Podcast show landing. Video course. Music album release. Virtual event. Documentary. Audiobook. Tutorial series. Interview series. Live stream event. Each composes audio or video into a full page-template you can use as-is.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cat-card">
          <div class="cat-num">16</div>
          <h3>Audio + video sections</h3>
          <p>Spotify playlist. SoundCloud track. Podcast hero. Episode archive. Listen-on strip. Album hero. Video testimonials grid. Course lessons. Single lesson with transcript. Webinar landing. Case study. YouTube channel hero. Live stream. Autoplay-bg hero. Featured episodes carousel. Audio testimonial.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cat-card">
          <div class="cat-num">11</div>
          <h3>Premium e-commerce</h3>
          <p>Story-led product page. Limited drop launch. Bundle builder. Gift guide. Subscription / recurring. Wholesale / B2B. Stockists locator. Sustainability page. Made-to-order configurator. Care guide. Loyalty / VIP program.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cat-card">
          <div class="cat-num">8</div>
          <h3>Premium heroes</h3>
          <p>Animated counter stats. Editorial split cover. Video bg + caption strip. Magazine cover. Countdown launch. Marquee announcement bar. Quote-led with portrait. Layered overlay card.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cat-card">
          <div class="cat-num">7</div>
          <h3>Composite sections</h3>
          <p>Above-the-fold (Hero + Logos + Stats in one insert). Social proof. Pricing block. Mid-page conversion. Pre-footer. About section. FAQ + final CTA. Multiple sections drop in pre-arranged.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="pricing" class="pricing">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Pricing — locked for life on the founder tier</h2>
      <p class="pricing-intro">The first 100 customers lock the founder price for the life of their active subscription. After 100, regular pricing kicks in. Annual subscription. No lifetime tier — the founder lock is your lifetime price.</p>
      <div class="tier-grid">
        <div class="tier-card">
          <div class="tier-label">Starter</div>
          <div class="tier-sites">1 site</div>
          <div class="tier-price founder">$49<span>/yr</span></div>
          <div class="tier-meta">Founder · first 100</div>
          <div class="tier-regular">$79/yr regular</div>
          <a href="https://pay.asteriscommerce.com/checkout/pro-patterns-starter" class="btn-primary">Get Starter</a>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-card featured">
          <div class="tier-flag">Most popular</div>
          <div class="tier-label">Pro</div>
          <div class="tier-sites">3 sites</div>
          <div class="tier-price founder">$99<span>/yr</span></div>
          <div class="tier-meta">Founder · first 100</div>
          <div class="tier-regular">$149/yr regular</div>
          <a href="https://pay.asteriscommerce.com/checkout/pro-patterns-pro" class="btn-primary">Get Pro</a>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-card">
          <div class="tier-label">Agency</div>
          <div class="tier-sites">5 sites</div>
          <div class="tier-price founder">$149<span>/yr</span></div>
          <div class="tier-meta">Founder · first 100</div>
          <div class="tier-regular">$229/yr regular</div>
          <a href="https://pay.asteriscommerce.com/checkout/pro-patterns-agency" class="btn-primary">Get Agency</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="includes">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">What you get</h2>
      <ul class="inc-list">
        <li>One-click access to all 73 patterns in the WordPress block inserter, under the <strong>Asteris — *</strong> categories</li>
        <li>Visible placeholder images on every empty image slot — no more blank canvases</li>
        <li>Free updates while your licence is active</li>
        <li>Premium support — 2-business-day response</li>
        <li>30-day money-back guarantee, no questions</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="compat">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Compatibility</h2>
      <ul class="inc-list">
        <li>Requires the free <strong>Asteris</strong> theme (download from wp.org once it lands)</li>
        <li>Requires WordPress 6.5+ and PHP 8.1+</li>
        <li>E-commerce patterns require WooCommerce (auto-detected; they hide cleanly if WC isn't active)</li>
        <li>A few section patterns use the free <strong>Asteris Blocks</strong> plugin for animated counters and similar — they fall back to static numbers if Blocks isn't installed</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="faq">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Frequently asked questions</h2>
      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Why a separate plugin instead of bundling everything in the free theme?</h3>
          <p>The free Asteris theme has ~110 patterns already — more than most premium themes. We chose to keep the free theme generous and put net-new specialty work in this paid product. Nothing was moved from free to paid. Pro Patterns is pure addition.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Can I use these patterns commercially?</h3>
          <p>Yes. Use them on client sites within your licence's site limit (1, 3, or 5 depending on your tier).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What happens if I cancel?</h3>
          <p>Patterns stay registered while you're licensed. After cancellation, the patterns stop appearing in the inserter on your sites — but any pages where you already used them keep working. Their content lives in WordPress's database like any other block content.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Will you add more patterns?</h3>
          <p>Yes. Regular drops — composite landing-page combos, dark-mode companions, more niche industries. All free while you're subscribed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Why is there no lifetime tier?</h3>
          <p>Because we want to keep shipping updates, and lifetime kills the recurring revenue that funds that work. The founder lock gives you the price certainty you'd get from lifetime, without crippling our ability to keep building.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="final-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Get started — $49/yr</h2>
      <p>Founder pricing locked for life. First 100 customers.</p>
      <a href="https://pay.asteriscommerce.com/checkout/pro-patterns-starter" class="btn-primary big">Get Pro Patterns →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  :root {
    --violet: #AA00FF;
    --violet-soft: rgba(170, 0, 255, 0.10);
    --violet-border: rgba(170, 0, 255, 0.32);
  }

  .container { max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 32px; }

  .hero { padding: 96px 0 72px; }
  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-block; color: var(--violet); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 64px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1.05;
    margin: 0 0 20px; color: #0a0a0a;
  }
  .lead { font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.55; max-width: 760px; color: #4a5568; margin: 0 0 32px; }
  .cta-row { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--violet); color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px;
    padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 120ms, transform 100ms; display: inline-block;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: #BD2FFF; transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn-primary.big { font-size: 18px; padding: 16px 36px; }
  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent; color: #1a1a1a; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;
    padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid #d8dce6;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--violet); color: var(--violet); }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin: 0 0 32px;
    color: #0a0a0a;
  }

  .categories { padding: 64px 0; background: #fafbfd; border-top: 1px solid #e0e3eb; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e3eb; }
  .cat-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
  .cat-card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e0e3eb; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px; }
  .cat-num { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--violet); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .cat-card h3 { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 10px; color: #0a0a0a; }
  .cat-card p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4a5568; margin: 0; }

  .pricing { padding: 80px 0; background: #fff; }
  .pricing-intro { text-align: center; font-size: 16px; color: #4a5568; max-width: 720px; margin: -16px auto 40px; line-height: 1.6; }
  .tier-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .tier-card { border: 1px solid #e0e3eb; border-radius: 14px; padding: 32px 28px; text-align: center; background: #fff; position: relative; }
  .tier-card.featured { border-color: var(--violet); border-width: 2px; transform: scale(1.03); }
  .tier-flag {
    position: absolute; top: -14px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: var(--violet); color: #fff; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 5px 14px; border-radius: 99px;
  }
  .tier-label { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #6b7280; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
  .tier-sites { font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 4px; }
  .tier-price { font-size: 48px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--violet); margin: 16px 0 6px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .tier-price span { font-size: 18px; color: #6b7280; font-weight: 500; }
  .tier-meta { font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .tier-regular { font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; margin: 6px 0 22px; text-decoration: line-through; }
  .tier-card .btn-primary { width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; }

  .includes, .compat { padding: 64px 0; background: #fafbfd; border-top: 1px solid #e0e3eb; }
  .compat { background: #fff; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e3eb; }
  .inc-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; max-width: 720px; }
  .inc-list li { padding: 12px 0 12px 28px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eef0f5; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.55; color: #1a1a1a; position: relative; }
  .inc-list li:before { content: "✓"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--violet); font-weight: 700; }
  .inc-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .faq { padding: 80px 0; background: #fafbfd; border-top: 1px solid #e0e3eb; }
  .faq-grid { display: grid; gap: 24px; max-width: 880px; }
  .faq-item { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e0e3eb; border-radius: 10px; padding: 24px 28px; }
  .faq-item h3 { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 10px; color: #0a0a0a; }
  .faq-item p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4a5568; margin: 0; }

  .final-cta { padding: 96px 0; text-align: center; background: #fff; }
  .final-cta h2 { font-size: 42px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 12px; color: #0a0a0a; }
  .final-cta p { font-size: 17px; color: #4a5568; margin: 0 0 28px; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 { font-size: 44px; }
    .lead { font-size: 18px; }
    .section-title { font-size: 26px; }
    .tier-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 380px; }
    .tier-card.featured { transform: none; }
    .final-cta h2 { font-size: 30px; }
  }
</style>
